          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1700036001694-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and your<strong> tomato paste </strong>in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml] </span>of <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>cooked rice </strong>with your <strong>pitted black olives</strong>,<strong> </strong>the juice of <strong>half </strong>your<strong> lemon[s]</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and the<strong> tomato stock</strong> and stir it all together</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min further or until everything is warmed through – this is your <strong>one pot</strong> <strong>chorizo, mixed pepper & tomato rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1700036006245-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
