      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one pot chorizo, mixed pepper & tomato rice</strong> garnished with the <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
